      <data key="d8">EXHAUST</data>
      <data key="d9">COMPLEMENTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The pathway principle depends on a clear route from contaminant source to the exhaust point, making exhaust placement and function central to the control strategy.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b_chunk_3</data>
      <data key="d14">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b</data>
