      <data key="d9">HAS_ADVERSE_EFFECT</data>
      <data key="d10">Air stream interruption disrupts the desired source-to-exhaust pathway, which the excerpt indicates makes contaminants less well controlled.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
